Twittergrab module for Drupal 7.x.
This module grabs your trends from Twitter.

INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS
-------------------------
1.  Copy the files included in the zip-file into a directory named "twittergrab" in
    your Drupal sites/all/modules/ directory.
2.  Login as site administrator.
3.  Enable the "twittergrab" module on the Administer -> Site
    building -> Modules page.
4.  Import the twittergrab.sql files for a sample configuration.
5.  Enjoy.